---
import whatsapp from "../../public/WhatsappLogo.svg"
---

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
    <p class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl uppercase font-bold">Entenda como atuamos:</p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-4 w-full">
            <li class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 md:p-8 border border-white rounded-sm text-white text-center flex items-center justify-center">1) Envie documentos e a notificação pelo WhatsApp.</li>
            <li class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 md:p-8 border border-white rounded-sm text-white text-center flex items-center justify-center">2) Analisamos o contrato e a fase do processo.</li>
            <li class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 md:p-8 border border-white rounded-sm text-white text-center flex items-center justify-center">3) Orientamos os próximos passos e custos aproximados.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <a class="inline-flex w-full max-w-xs md:w-auto justify-center bg-[#B9B4AB] text-black px-4 py-3 md:px-3 md:py-2 rounded-sm items-center gap-2 transition transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#B9B4AB] whitespace-nowrap" href="https://wa.me/5592984093014?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20quero%20avaliar%20meu%20caso" aria-label="Abrir WhatsApp">
                <img src={whatsapp.src} alt="WhatsApp" class="w-5 h-5" />
                <span>Enviar pelo WhatsApp</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>